// 4. We store PNR and vendor booking ID for tracking
// 5. If vendor rejects, we handle refund (since payment already succeeded)
//
// Why vendor booking after payment? This is the "ghost booking" pattern:
// - We take payment first (user commitment)
// - Then book with vendor (fulfillment)
// - If vendor fails, we refund (user gets money back)
